{"tid":1381542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰術檢討] 有無人 想嬴番一場 前線入","createTime":"2019-07-29T09:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T06:26:35.000Z","uid":252510,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7470c024973569c713e551492d074276c2e24c19","tid":1381542,"uid":252510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:08:10.000Z","msg":"首先，我唔認同武力上既勝利 = 整場運動上既勝利<br />\n但我相信, 要比呢個不義政權睇到, 我地唔係單方面被武力壓制, 光復香港唔係單單一個口號<br />\n<br />\n當然最理想既方式係目標式進攻, 快速完成任務後就全體撤退, 好似7.1咁, 唔需要硬碰硬<br />\n但當 情況唔理想, 需要對峙, 硬碰硬時, 我希望各位手足能夠有一套應對手法共識, 而唔係企係到等人清/用血肉之驅硬碰<br />\n<br />\n我地要認清自己同對方既優劣<br />\n以子之強，攻彼之弱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地要建立一套迎戰方式，嬴一次就夠!!!</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求討論<br />\n<br />\n其他兄弟睇法<br />\n[打機戰術 有圖］遠攻好撚緊要  全部玩坦冇鬼用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dsczkT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dsczkT</a><br />\n<br />\n《兵法撚》勇武派樽頸 兵法破速龍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1381408</a><br />\n<br />\n［戰略導向］［由 準。勇武邁向 真。勇武］遊擊戰將由be water 升級至hit and run<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/drNikT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/drNikT</a><br />\n<br />\n前線，今晚好撚嬲，再係咁唔好問點解愈黎愈少前線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dshhzT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dshhzT</a>"},{"pid":"06822084e8c91d9430aafef9d51f72d473cd3553","tid":1381542,"uid":252510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:08:37.000Z","msg":"有無人有其他諗法"},{"pid":"5ebe3d73e5fb1e67c3cb71d0d96e4b94e8d44274","tid":1381542,"uid":252510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:08:49.000Z","msg":"求討論"},{"pid":"86a9047c99fc53364de266bbc868b8b9bca53beb","tid":1381542,"uid":263161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:08:58